# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# AlpacaVision AI — .gitignore
# Public repo = code + configs + paper sources + metrics JSON.
# Heavy artefacts (data, models, venvs) live on Zenodo / GitHub Releases.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.egg-info/
dist/
build/
.eggs/
*.egg

# Virtual environments (Windows venv/ and Linux .venv-linux/)
venv/
env/
.conda/
.venv/
.venv-linux/

# Secrets — never commit
.env
*.key
kaggle.json

# Jupyter
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# Tooling cache
.pytest_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.mypy_cache/

# Data — all of it is heavy; goes to Zenodo (CC BY 4.0), never to git
data/

# Trained models & exports — go to GitHub Releases / Hugging Face
models/**/*.pt
models/**/*.onnx
models/**/*.tflite
models/pretrained/

# Outputs — ignore heavy run data, KEEP figures + metrics JSON for the paper
outputs/training_runs/
outputs/predictions/
outputs/reports/
outputs/figures/stage1_test_eval/
!outputs/figures/

# Ultralytics run dirs & logs
runs/
logs/
*.log

# Root-level stray weights / archives
/*.pt
/*.onnx
*.zip
*.tar.gz

# Paper — keep sources (.tex/.bib/.cls/.bst/.sty + logos + figures), drop build files
paper/manuscript/manuscript.pdf
paper/cover_letter/*.pdf
paper/manuscript/*.aux
paper/manuscript/*.bbl
paper/manuscript/*.blg
paper/manuscript/*.out
paper/manuscript/*.log
paper/manuscript/*.toc
paper/manuscript/*.spl
paper/**/*-eps-converted-to.pdf

# IDE / OS
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Local office drafts (Anexos etc.) — not part of the code repo
/*.docx
/*.png

# Legacy / archived (superseded files kept locally, not published)
**/legacy/
INICIAR.bat
_local/
NuevasImagenes/
paper/figures/_old_replaced/
